Next we move to the **Add Transaction screen**.
This screen determines **whether the product lives or dies**.

Right now your design looks clean, but from a product standpoint it’s **slow, redundant, and cognitively heavy**. A finance app must allow users to record an expense in **2–3 seconds**. Yours requires **too many decisions before the user even finishes typing the amount**.

