# Milestone 6 — Habit Loop & Daily Engagement

Screen: **Daily Review**

Goal:
Create a **daily ritual** that keeps users returning to the app.

Users should open the app and immediately see:

```
what happened today
whether they stayed on track
what to fix tomorrow
```

This screen turns the app from **a ledger** into **a daily reflection tool**.

---

# Task 1 — Introduce Daily Review Entry Point

## Problem

Right now users have no reason to open the app unless they spend money.

That means **low engagement**.

---

## Component: Daily Review Card

Shown when opening the app.

