# Brutal Truth

Right now your app assumes users will:

```
remember
care
stay disciplined
```

That assumption is wrong.

Users only stick to financial tracking when the app builds a **habit loop**:

```
trigger → action → reward
```

Right now your product only provides **the action**.

No trigger.
No reward.

And without those, even a perfectly designed finance app will be abandoned.

